# Screenshots

## Purpose

This section contains screenshots demonstrating the successful implementation of the **"Optimizing User, Group, and Role Management with Access Control and Workflows"** project in ServiceNow.

The screenshots provide visual proof of the system configuration, role assignments, access control implementation, workflow automation, and testing.

