Testing Summary

The screenshots confirm that:

- Users and roles were successfully configured.
- Groups were created correctly.
- ACLs restricted unauthorized access.
- Flow Designer automated task assignment.
- Project Managers had full access.
- Team Members had limited access.
- The project met all functional requirements.
